{"tid":2051392,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港嘅日本藝人 請大家支持soko!","createTime":"2020-06-04T17:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T03:07:00.000Z","uid":225542,"like":152,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"d722630bde4cb46fb8cf46ee2d9cc4f457393fcb","tid":2051392,"uid":225542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"身為日本人嘅Soko 一直都關心住香港嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n人離鄉賤，落魄嘅Soko可以話藝人嘅仕途坎坷，不論係日本定香港都好，好似努力同收成都唔成正比。<br />\n<br />\n係依個情況下，佢冇選擇明哲保身好似其他奶共後生tvb藝員，或者屎家閪班垃圾，有人唔做走去奶屎眼做狗，有事就扮睇唔到，繼續開心share high tea posts，或者得閑打句「好嬲」<br />\n<br />\n雖則唔係話要鬥黃，每個人都有佢嘅自由去表態或不表態，但佢選擇放低身份，甚至前途去表態同行動，係好多人都做唔到。<br />\n<br />\n我欣賞佢嘅努力，同肯入鄉隨俗，唔似其他同行，以利益行先<br />\n<br />\n所以希望多啲人欣賞佢同關注佢 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/sokoizumi?igshid=4ea57jkmux33\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsokoizumi%3Figshid%3D4ea57jkmux33&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=e40d4d8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/sokoizumi?igshid=4ea57jkmux33</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zV-djo1JRCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzV-djo1JRCo&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=8a82a1fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zV-djo1JRCo</a>"},{"pid":"bea5edcc4ddc918fc3e8ba49da5675add4cd237e","tid":2051392,"uid":71676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:52:21.000Z","msg":"Sogo san<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3c09e00778e844d6d90be99ca57faf8ec2b4a9","tid":2051392,"uid":225542,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"最欣賞係佢嘅真誠同不放棄嘅精神 <br />\n<br />\n香港好少咁嘅藝人"},{"pid":"5ff8d7a9d05cda1a221e76f14082e4744f8af4c6","tid":2051392,"uid":225542,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyT